fulltitle: The Birth of Bebop - Kenny Clarke
description:

The founders of Bebop were Charlie Parker, Dizzy Gillespie, Thelonious Monk, Bud Powell and Kenny Clarke.  Here, in 1970 interview with Danish television, drummer Kenny Clarke, aka "Klook," looks book.
title: The Birth of Bebop - Kenny Clarke
